    <h1><%= recipe.title %></h1>
    <h2>Here you will find the recipe for <%= recipe.title %>:</h2>

    <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>1 can chickpeasl</li>
        <li>2 tbps tahini</li>
        <li>2 cloves garil, minced</li>
        <li>Juice of 1 lemon</li>
        <li>2 tbsp of olive oil</li>
        <li>Salt to taste</li>
        <li>Fresh Parsley for garnish</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Instructions:</h2>
    <p>
        1. In a food processor, combine chickpeas, tahini, garlic, lemon juice, and olive oil.
        <br>
        2. Blend until smooth, adding water as needed for desired consistency.
        <br>
        3. Season with salt and serve with pita bread or veggies.
    </p>
  

